---
import { getCollection } from 'astro:content';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Angelo Alberico - Sviluppatore & Studente UNISA</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        nav {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto 3rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 2rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 3rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            color: #667eea;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .intro {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .tech-stack {
            margin: 2rem 0;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .tech-stack h3 {
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .tech-stack ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .tech-stack li {
            padding: 0.5rem;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding-left: 1.5rem;
            position: relative;
        }

        .tech-stack li:before {
            content: "→";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #667eea;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .cta-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .cta-buttons a {
            padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 6px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        }

        .cta-primary {
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
        }

        .cta-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
        }

        .cta-secondary {
            background: transparent;
            color: #667eea;
            border: 2px solid #667eea;
        }

        .cta-secondary:hover {
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <a href="/">About</a>
        <a href="/projects">Projects</a>
        <a href="/repositories">Repositories</a>
        <a href="/cv">CV</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>Angelo Alberico</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Sviluppatore Web & Studente UNISA</p>

        <div class="intro">
            <p>Ciao! Sono uno studente appassionato di <strong>sviluppo web</strong> e <strong>algoritmi</strong> presso l'Università di Salerno (UNISA). 
            Mi piace creare soluzioni innovative e contribuire a progetti che fanno la differenza.</p>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">Attualmente collaboro con <strong>ISISLab</strong> su progetti come <strong>WRF4Salerno</strong>, 
            un sistema di previsione meteorologica ad alta risoluzione per il territorio campano.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="tech-stack">
            <h3>Tecnologie & Skills</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Frontend: React, Vue.js, Astro, Tailwind CSS</li>
                <li>Backend: Node.js, Python, Java</li>
                <li>Database: PostgreSQL, MongoDB</li>
                <li>Tools: Git, Docker, Linux</li>
                <li>Data Science: NumPy, Pandas, scikit-learn</li>
                <li>IoT & Embedded: Arduino, RaspberryPi</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-buttons">
            <a href="/projects" class="cta-primary">Vedi i miei progetti</a>
            <a href="/repositories" class="cta-secondary">GitHub</a>
            <a href="/cv" class="cta-secondary">Scarica CV</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
